These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, folk, reggae, classical
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of reggae and the fan of classical##2
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | classical | folk | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | 7up | lemonade | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | lizard | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, pear, cherry, artichoke
1. the person eating cherry is between the person eating pear and the person eating cranberry##2
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | artichoke | pear | cherry | cranberry |

